  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0bb5\u0b9a\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0bb4\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0b8e\u0ba9 \u0b89\u0bb2\u0b95 \u0bb5\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf \u0ba4\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "World Bank informs that it will not provide new financial facilities",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The World Bank has announced yesterday (28) that it will not provide new financial facilities to Sri Lanka until an adequate economic policy framework is implemented in Sri Lanka.",
        "The announcement by the World Bank suggests that deep structural reforms are needed with a focus on creating economic stability.",
        "The announcement also states that the structural causes of the current economic crisis in Sri Lanka should also be addressed.",
        "The World Bank has expressed deep concern over the current economic crisis in Sri Lanka and its impact on the people of Sri Lanka.",
        "Funding projects already approved by the World Bank to provide medicines, gas, fertilizer, food for schoolchildren and cash assistance to the most vulnerable families in Sri Lanka to overcome acute shortages of essential commodities for poor and vulnerable families in Sri Lanka, the World Bank announced, will reallocate resources.",
        "As of yesterday (28), the World Bank has indicated that the United States has restructured and released $160 million for emergency needs.",
        "Working closely with institutions and organizations to provide the necessary support to poor and most vulnerable families, the World Bank is monitoring projects implemented with World Bank assistance, the World Bank said in a statement."
      ],
